Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.73,0:01:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,None of us are bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.59,0:01:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Mizuguchi from the basketball team or me...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.67,0:01:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Or you, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.36,0:01:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,There are no bad people anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.59,0:01:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But bad things happen to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.65,0:01:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know why?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.29,0:01:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it a conspiracy?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.53,0:01:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.80,0:02:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Some enormous organization has been plotting evil conspiracies against us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.17,0:02:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.77,0:02:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.97,0:02:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard it through the grapevine the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.77,0:02:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai, today's the last day you'll come to this club room.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.14,0:02:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You've played cards with me for the last two years, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.21,0:03:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been four years, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.74,0:03:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Four years and four months, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.68,0:03:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.65,0:03:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't look so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.05,0:03:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.66,0:03:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't I give you some medicine or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.72,0:03:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Medicine, you said?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.29,0:03:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's mood-altering medicine. You'll feel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.82,0:03:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,If you've been suffering from lack of sleep, I recommend sleeping pills.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.53,0:03:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you're depressed, take an antidepressant.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.39,0:03:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And this one is a mood-stabilizing medication.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.70,0:03:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.37,0:03:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai, how many doctors do you have?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.53,0:03:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.06,0:03:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Three right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.78,0:03:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Being a working adult is tough, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.25,0:04:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Being a student preparing for a college exam is tough, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.56,0:04:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing now, Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.96,0:04:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Working at a ward office.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.16,0:04:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So you work for the government? That's pretty cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.26,0:04:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you, Sato?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.33,0:04:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently you've got time to wander around on a weekday carrying all that stuff with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.21,0:04:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,A part-time worker?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.61,0:04:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I was a part-time worker...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.21,0:04:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't know how to put it,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.85,0:04:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'm, err...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.84,0:04:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a hikikomori!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.56,0:04:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And inside of the bag, I have...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.51,0:04:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.52,0:04:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Ero games!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.59,0:04:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Figurines!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.19,0:04:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,DVDs!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.38,0:04:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And all kinds of miscellaneous anime-related products!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.46,0:04:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a typical otaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.03,0:04:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I spent all my money for next month's rent on these!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.29,0:04:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm like, "what am I gonna do now," you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.35,0:04:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.67,0:04:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already been a hikikomori for four years.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.54,0:04:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Call me the Master of Hikikomori!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.44,0:04:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I'd already kind of guessed that that's what you're like.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.20,0:05:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.42,0:05:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe that's what your opinion of me was.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.99,0:05:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I was only half serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.02,0:05:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know, I still think about it every now and then,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.13,0:05:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,about my junior in high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.79,0:05:17.79,Note,,0,0,0,,Literature Club
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.50,0:05:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,He'd tell me about his buddies a lot, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.74,0:05:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I never saw anyone come visit him at the club room.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.28,0:05:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I can still picture that image clearly in my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.09,0:05:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We should've made it more official and dated each other back then, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.88,0:05:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We probably had better things to do than just playing cards every single day, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.02,0:05:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,If we would've had a healthy romantic relationship, maybe you never would've become a hikikomori.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.40,0:05:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.94,0:06:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is a conspiracy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.67,0:06:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I see, that's what I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.83,0:06:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.76,0:06:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Please come check it out inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.57,0:06:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that your cell phone, Sato?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.68,0:06:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.49,0:06:35.12,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&HB4B5AC&\frz359\pos(841.349,518.824)}Yamazaki
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.21,0:06:35.45,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&HB4B5AC&\frz359\pos(873.707,543.025)}0 sec
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.78,0:06:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Where the hell are you, Sato?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.89,0:06:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been calling you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.24,0:06:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be waiting for you at the same spot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.35,0:06:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,If you take too much longer, I'm just gonna head back without you! Got it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.93,0:06:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, he's scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.32,0:06:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Yamazaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.46,0:06:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you still remember that time, right before you graduated,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.93,0:06:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,when I rescued that middle school kid who was being bullied?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.60,0:07:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Now he's living in the apartment right next to mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.47,0:07:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And today, he brought me here with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.89,0:07:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, a hikikomori guy like me wouldn't be wandering around in a place like this, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.68,0:07:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me your cell phone number.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.82,0:07:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.74,0:07:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.36,0:07:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Tatsuhiro Sato, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.34,0:07:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.49,0:07:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember my first name?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.09,0:07:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,, Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.84,0:07:31.26,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&HB4B5AC&\fs30.253\frz359\pos(611.236,187.563)}Kashiwa, Hitomi
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.73,0:07:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I can contact you any time I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.65,0:07:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,How convenient things have become, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.14,0:07:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If you go to a convenience store you can buy food, drinks, cosmetics,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.40,0:07:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,even cell phones.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.52,0:07:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But they don't sell relationships.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.05,0:07:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Sato...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.39,0:07:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I see you again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.75,0:08:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I was totally lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.50,0:08:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Who'd have thought that I'd find so much Pururin stuff
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.40,0:08:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,at some store I happened to stop by while looking for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.91,0:08:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's all rare stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.18,0:08:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if someone who actually worked on the show sold all the stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.88,0:08:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's make use of the blessings received on today's pilgrimage to the Holy Land
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.73,0:08:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and get our noses to the grindstone making that game!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.46,0:08:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously, the Holy Land is the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.46,0:08:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I can feel my inspiration flowing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.50,0:08:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I see you again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.43,0:08:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.00,0:08:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're right, you're a hikikomori. I forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.88,0:08:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.81,0:08:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I see you again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.07,0:08:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're a hikikomori, right, Sato?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.30,0:09:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Something hit me when I was in the Holy Land!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.56,0:09:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on, the freckles are in!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.49,0:09:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Characters with freckles are coming at you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.40,0:09:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We can do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.63,0:09:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We can totally finish it up before the production deadline, Sato!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.53,0:09:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten days until the deadline...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.26,0:09:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Any game made in ten days time isn't going to be much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.74,0:09:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But if I give it to Misaki, my promise to her will be fulfilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.11,0:09:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,She would never bother me again, and I'd go back to my hikikomori life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.85,0:09:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I see you again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.81,0:09:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a hikikomori, right, Sato?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.22,0:09:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Sato... Sato... Sato...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.85,0:09:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The only problem left is your script!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.24,0:09:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,If you just start doing little bits of it and then give them to me as you go, I could manage to...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.37,0:09:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Yamazaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.54,0:09:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.29,0:10:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure she's thinking I'm pretty weird even now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.17,0:10:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanna know how to escape being a hikikomori, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.00,0:10:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.00,0:10:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you once you sign the contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.04,0:10:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's really possible that she could...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.47,0:10:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This could be your last chance, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.88,0:10:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Sign this and bring it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.85,0:10:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The appointment is ten days from now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.22,0:10:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's pointless for me to wait on her like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.99,0:10:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.66,0:10:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But if she really is the goddess who appeared to rescue me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.22,0:10:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Sato!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.55,0:11:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,She really came!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.69,0:11:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.93,0:11:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You still have ten days till the appointment.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.40,0:11:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you bring the game by any chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.40,0:11:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,No, the e.g. I was making has been canceled.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.81,0:11:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Making? I thought you said you were going to bring the one that you made in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.94,0:11:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I meant, the one that I'm working on is about to be canceled.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.28,0:11:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.15,0:11:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, what is "e.g."?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.43,0:11:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's short for EROA and GARIOA!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.84,0:11:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Essentially, EROA stands for, "Economic Rehabilitation in Occupied Area Fund"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.99,0:11:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and GARIOA for, "Government and Relief in Occupied Areas."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.12,0:11:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,After World War II, America provided funding
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.81,0:11:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,in order to prevent social unrest caused by illness and starvation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.60,0:12:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Does a game like that really sell?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.64,0:12:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a big lie, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.19,0:12:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.14,0:12:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Your being a creator was a lie too, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.65,0:12:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.43,0:12:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is that you're unemployed and a hikikomori, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.04,0:12:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a deal, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.30,0:12:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you're going to be fine, Sato!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.10,0:12:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,With a little training, you'll be able to get out into that big world out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.71,0:12:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.47,0:12:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,A kindhearted girl who rescues young people who are suffering!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.09,0:12:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to start your counseling tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.96,0:12:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't skip it no matter what, okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.13,0:13:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,If you break the promise, you'll have to pay me a million yen as a penalty!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.31,0:13:55.56,Note,,0,0,0,,Note: #003 reads "Kashiwa, Hitomi". All the rest are Yamazaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.09,0:13:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd better apologize to Yamazaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.19,0:14:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet he's pissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.96,0:14:05.86,Background2,,0,0,0,,Don't give me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.49,0:14:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,He's pissed...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.66,0:14:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He's very pissed...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.99,0:14:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,How did this conversation come to that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.45,0:14:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, I moved here with the money I made!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.12,0:14:18.62,Background2,,0,0,0,,I don't have to follow your orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.62,0:14:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he talking to his parents or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.10,0:14:22.41,Background2,,0,0,0,,What? That's none of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.41,0:14:25.26,Background2,,0,0,0,,Listen, I will not take over your farm!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.82,0:14:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess he has his own problems too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.80,0:15:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.39,0:15:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hi...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.08,0:15:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahem!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.36,0:15:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'd like to commence the first seminar on "How to Escape the Hikikomori State."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.02,0:15:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,First, a general overview on what it is to be a hikikomori...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.82,0:15:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Say...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.94,0:15:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.78,0:15:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.03,0:15:31.53,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\fs72.605\pos(533.933,93.781)\frz23.646\fax-0.1}SECRET NOTES
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.89,0:15:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Secret notes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.54,0:15:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I said, what is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.95,0:15:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Secret notes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.65,0:15:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not what I'm asking!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.18,0:15:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you can't look, Sato!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.32,0:15:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's secret!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.59,0:15:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.45,0:15:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Moving on... What are the causes of hikikomorism?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.40,0:15:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Based on the results of my research,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.38,0:15:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,hikikomorism can arise from incompatibility with one's environment.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.22,0:16:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, it's a type of mental problem, caused by an inability to function in society.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.17,0:16:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That is why it is important to know how to come to terms with society.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.02,0:16:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,For example...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.57,0:16:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,God.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.57,0:16:15.08,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\bord0.756\c&HB2FFFF&\fnFormal 436 BT\fs102.858\pos(640,234.454)}GOD
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.90,0:16:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Since time immemorial,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.41,0:16:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,people have resolved dissatisfactions with the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.26,0:16:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and controlled their emotions by believing in and worshipping gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.93,0:16:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And for that reason there are many different gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.84,0:16:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It is said that there are as many as eight million gods in Japan...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.17,0:16:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Eight million? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.84,0:16:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that just too many, don't you think? Eight million...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.97,0:16:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on a sec...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.20,0:16:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that supposed to be "countless gods"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.29,0:16:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's spelled "eight million" but it really means "countless."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.56,0:16:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.26,0:16:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So there are countless gods...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.69,0:16:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So basically, there are so many gods!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.47,0:16:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahem...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.53,0:17:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Many people are saved from their pain and suffering thanks to these gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.25,0:17:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,However, that's not the case for some people.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.49,0:17:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Those people seek salvation in stuff like "philosophy."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.17,0:17:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Now! I know this is sudden, but let's psychoanalyze you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.01,0:17:20.22,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an7}Illustrated!!\NFascinating Psychoanalysis\NBy Dr. Freud
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.33,0:17:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,A guy name Freud came up with this,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.55,0:17:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and supposedly it became very popular around the 19th century.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.88,0:17:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure all that scholarly stuff from earlier was too difficult for you to understand,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.35,0:17:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,since you're a college-dropout and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.50,0:17:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.32,0:17:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But this part is easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.09,0:17:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Your problem will disappear by talking about the dream you had this morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.70,0:17:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll analyze it for you, so please explain what happened in the dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.21,0:17:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This brat...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.64,0:17:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Does she think I don't even know who Freud is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.68,0:17:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's what she thinks, she can analyze to her heart's content!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.81,0:17:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,There was an enormous and rough-looking snake.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.10,0:18:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The snake went under the water,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.64,0:18:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and I thrust a huge sword into an apple.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.33,0:18:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I shot off a beautiful shiny black gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.86,0:18:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Snake... Ocean...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.05,0:18:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Apple... Sword... Gun...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.65,0:18:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We're done with Freud!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.99,0:18:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Next is Jung!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.08,0:18:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,No, forget about Jung.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.57,0:18:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the results of the dream analysis?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.67,0:18:39.39,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an7}Easy to Understand\NJung
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.14,0:18:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Jung!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.14,0:18:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Supposedly this guy had a disagreement with Freud and struck out in another direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.88,0:18:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I said! What about the rough-looking snake?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.79,0:18:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the sword? What about the gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.17,0:18:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What do they symbolize?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.06,0:18:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to hear that from you, Misaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.17,0:18:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.13,0:18:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I said it's time for Jung right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.49,0:19:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can't listen to me, then today's seminar ends right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.72,0:19:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to do the rest tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.06,0:19:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.36,0:19:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't expecting much from it anyway, but still...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.94,0:19:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh well, I guess I'll stick around for a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.01,0:19:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,since a breach of contract means a million yen penalty.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.06,0:19:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a hikikomori, right, Sato?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.59,0:19:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,There is reason for which I'm thankful to have met Misaki though.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.78,0:19:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I've realized something as I talked to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.91,0:19:49.08,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\fnCourier New\fs36.303\pos(490.786,502.185)}Scenario-01.txt
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.80,0:19:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I seclude myself in my room,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.12,0:19:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,as long as I'm doing something with a goal in mind, I'm not a hikikomori!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.42,0:20:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yamazaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.19,0:20:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's open!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.40,0:20:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw Misaki and talked to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.31,0:20:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I told her the truth about my being a hikikomori.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.01,0:20:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to admit that I didn't think we could make a decent game in ten days.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.65,0:20:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all because of the delay in your script writing part, isn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.16,0:20:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to quit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.05,0:20:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I've collected sound effects for free and even programs.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.89,0:20:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as we have the script,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.35,0:20:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,we should be able to make it happen if we work intensively!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.15,0:20:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as we have the script!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.00,0:20:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yamazaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.13,0:20:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.80,0:20:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna quit either.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.81,0:21:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,My promise to Misaki is over with, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.45,0:21:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's exactly why we should take our time
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.20,0:21:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,and make something good without worrying about a deadline!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.28,0:21:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Sato...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.63,0:21:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the story for the game that I've come up with.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.52,0:21:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I wrote down some characters' names too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.89,0:21:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,They're nothing like the ones in the games you'd see at the store though.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.49,0:21:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, I'm a loser and I admit that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.27,0:21:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just an unemployed hikikomori man.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.34,0:21:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But if I can finish making this game,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.27,0:21:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I could be a better man!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.88,0:21:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Sato...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.17,0:21:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's make it! Let's make our game!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.02,0:21:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.96,0:21:59.96,Note,,0,0,0,,{\c&HFDFBF5&\pos(640,136.135)\fs60.504}Episode 05
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.96,0:21:59.96,Note,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,468.907)\fs60.504\c&HE3DFCF&}Welcome to Counseling!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.64,0:23:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You should definitely play it too, Nanako!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.88,0:23:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That is looking down on others.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.74,0:23:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,How am I gonna get home now?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.70,0:23:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Next episode, "Welcome to the Classroom!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.70,0:23:39.96,Note,,0,0,0,,{\c&HACEE9D&\pos(640,113.445)\fs60.504}Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.70,0:23:39.96,Note,,0,0,0,,{\c&H68FE19&\pos(640,446.219)\fs60.504}Welcome to the Classroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.01,0:00:16.18,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,I lift my eyes a little and look into the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.34,0:00:19.26,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,All I do is mutter every time,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.33,0:00:22.31,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,as I turn my back
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.31,0:00:24.64,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,on this perfect everyday life
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.64,0:00:27.81,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,"Where am I supposed to go?"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.98,0:00:32.86,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,With you who are giving me a look like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.28,0:00:42.20,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,In the shadows of a back alley,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.12,0:00:49.33,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,the hands of a clock repaint the time that has been stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.15,0:00:53.07,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,Extended hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.19,0:00:57.44,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,puzzle pieces that don't fit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.95,0:01:01.74,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,Until the abandoned two
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.74,0:01:05.79,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,reunite with something
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.04,0:01:10.42,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,that has been lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.42,0:01:13.96,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,Recover
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.17,0:01:18.22,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,the last piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.09,0:01:24.35,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,and let's start walking.
